<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-96-0406 </DOCNO><TEXT>The FTU vacuum vassel has been designed to withstand high electromagneticand thermal loads and to reach high vacuum conditions which are essentialto obtain clean, impurity free plasma. After a survey of the vacuum chamberrequirements and of the design development, the paper reports the mainmanufactoring process such as welding, stress relieving, machining, nondestructivetesting, outgassing and preassembly.</TEXT></DOC>